Bachelor topic title:
    Web application for Online Business Promotion

Description of the problem:
    Towards managing the data needed by all the users for interacting with the application we must have
    an unique connection to a database.

Advantages:
    - unique instance of the connection to a certain database
    - easy to manage the access to the data

Disadvantages:
    - the overall performance of the application may be affected by the presence of only one connection
    - the pattern may affect the processes of unit testing

